title.rendered: How to unlock Sony Vaio bios Password

content.rendered:
How to unlock Sony Vaio One-time bios Password

If you have a Sony Vaio 16 characters 4×4 we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen
  • Enter the wrong password three times
  • You will see a screen with KEY (xxxx–xxxx–xxxx–xxxx) and you will be asked for enter ONETIME PASSWORD.

  • Please Type your KEY  example see picture below (16 chars KEY e.g. V29F-R8TJ-DKX3-878K)

  • In this case, System Disable key is 16 chars KEY  V29F-R8TJ-DKX3-878K
  • Fill the fields below: your email, your KEY. After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • In Laptop: enter a calculated password, then push Enter key.

VERY IMPORTANT: Do not power off the computer once you provide us with a KEY (Key: xxxx–xxxx–xxxx–xxxx), wait for a one-time password. There’s a unique password for every KEY.Don’t turn off your notebook, don’t restart it, don’t enter anything except generated code.

Price for unlock 1 unit Sony One-time password is:    $ 12.00

How to unlock Sony Vaio with 7 digits serial number

If you have a Sony Vaio 7 digit serial number example ( 4494333 ) we will give you the possibility for you to remove the password from  BIOS

  • Power on your laptop and wait for the password screen

  • In this case, serial number is 4494333
  • Fill the fields below: your email , your KEY.
  • After this, click on the Send button to send at us the information
  • Then, after sending the necessary information, proceed with payment at Buy Now With PayPal.
  • After payment processing, your master password will be sent immediately (to your email and PayPal email address)
  • In Laptop: enter a calculated password, then push Enter key.

VERY IMPORTANT: Do not power off the computer once you provide us with a KEY (Key: xxxx–xxxx–xxxx–xxxx), wait for a one-time password. There’s a unique password for every KEY.Don’t turn off your notebook, don’t restart it, don’t enter anything except generated code.

Price for unlock 1 unit Sony 7 digit password is:    $ 9.00
